{"tid":505104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好懼怕死亡","createTime":"2017-12-20T18:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T05:01:26.000Z","uid":73531,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5f13a20b1bb67cecf5adff5aee8688b25cf4100b","tid":505104,"uid":73531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:27:04.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好怕死亡呢個term<br />\n因為覺得 死係一件好孤獨嘅事<br />\n呢個過程只可以自己去體驗<br />\n無論係屋企人定男朋友都唔會陪到我<br />\n亦冇人話到俾我知 呢樣嘢係點<br />\n<br />\n死前一刻到底有幾痛苦<br />\n死後係咪真係會歸零<br />\n假如無輪迴呢樣野 <br />\n每個人係咪係世上只會出現一次 <br />\n然後以後都唔會有「我」<br />\n<br />\n近排 無論新聞定身邊都<br />\n發生唔少關於死亡嘅事<br />\n又令我憶起對死亡嘅恐懼<br />\n一諗到自己遲早有一日會死<br />\n就覺得好恐怖<br />\n點解有人會有勇氣自動走向死亡？"},{"pid":"4ae44615a797206799310d7ddc3d5e817a7e519b","tid":505104,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:31:47.000Z","msg":"當世界冇野再值得留戀"},{"pid":"46a84039bff8c9e63ea2d93d98ed0ce5ef3ebe1d","tid":505104,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"d95abe8fcb3b6e845400728bc670a2379d6157c1","tid":505104,"uid":152047,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"你再諗真啲，生活上有更多比死亡更可怕嘅嘢，你就唔會畏懼死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1330248e187d7bca3949c27a2257f2ab98266a2","tid":505104,"uid":73531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當世界冇野再值得留戀</blockquote><br />\n我留戀我嘅生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd356f781015ca66ebeb8cf642464f2de38c3040","tid":505104,"uid":73531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T18:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你再諗真啲，生活上有更多比死亡更可怕嘅嘢，你就唔會畏懼死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n始終死亡係一樣未知嘅東西<br />\n我無辦法作出對比"},{"pid":"2ccf9117c86ff65d2d38d0784a2184d679401118","tid":505104,"uid":13184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"