pid":"eb4e875bfb240015de93cde14e4e4f4f0fbe5d62","tid":505104,"uid":145007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T19:12:37.000Z","msg":"的確 死亡真係好恐怖<br />\n雖然某啲信仰同你講 依個世界有天堂等等<br />\n但冇人可以測透死之後發生嘅事<br />\n不過正因如此 更加要珍惜刻下<br />\n去花心機去愛想愛嘅人 做你想做嘅事<br />\n因為冇人會知道自己幾時死<br />\n咁樣做嘅話 就算死 都死得無悔<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999"},{"pid":"26deb0d60a14e2b3625ff263a0ef5de1fc2e0a43","tid":505104,"uid":65629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T19:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6964ebfaaaf57a54173d06d1869c1afa7d95bce1","tid":505104,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T19:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會係到諗，以後既幾千億年會點，係咪永遠都會黑色一片，寂靜，諗到依一步就好驚。</blockquote><br />\n10既100次方年後，宇宙就會熱寂<br />\n咩都唔會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9206ab0941ebe7a591c8aee2a5c9cab69d0e85c7","tid":505104,"uid":44724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T19:17:31.000Z","msg":"充實過每一日 <br />\n與你喜歡的人相處每一日每一夜便足夠<br />\n做人應知足常樂，才會死而無憾"}]}